                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read, "Convicted on the 24th Sept., 1844, and trans<lb></lb>ported seven years"</hi>)—he is the boy.</p>
